      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> wholewheat noodles</strong> to a large bowl, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir for 10 secs to separate the noodles</p><p>Set aside to soak for 6 min</p><p>Drain the soaked noodles</p>",
