    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halved baby corn</strong> and roughly crumble the <strong>chestnut mushrooms </strong>into the pan</p><p>Then cook for 2-3 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
